      • drawRectangle

        void drawRectangle(int x,
                 int y,
                 int width,
                 int height,
                 java.awt.Color fillColor,
                 java.awt.Color strokeColor,
                 int strokeWidth)
        Draws a rectangle with top-left corner at [x,y] position. Rectangle has specified width and height, is filled with certain color and the line around the rectangle has its own color and thickness.
        Parameters:
        x - coordinate of top-left corner
        y - coordinate of top-left corner
        width - of the rectangle
        height - of the rectangle
        fillColor - color rectangle is filled with
        strokeColor - color of line around rectangle
        strokeWidth - thickness of line around the rectangle
